{"tid":2447694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紅隧內慢駛被控公眾妨礙 被告辯稱當時關節創傷 羅德泉: 審訊前不准駕駛","createTime":"2021-03-15T11:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T13:46:15.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"04d8a210ab692f73c551574c5a375cba54406236","tid":2447694,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:14:24.000Z","msg":"去年5月27日網民為反國歌法二讀而發起「5.27和你慢駛塞車大行動」，有助理工程師被指在海底隧道以時速10至15公里慢駛，造成阻塞一至二分鐘。他今在東區裁判法院<span class=\"red\">承認公眾妨礙等罪</span>，主任裁判官羅德泉先為其索取背景及社會服務令報告，准被告保釋至下月9日判刑。<span class=\"red\">同案中另一被告僅承認兩項涉及交通規例罪名，否認公眾妨礙罪</span>，裁判官聽過其抗辯理由後，以影響公眾安全為由，附加擔保條件，下令他保釋期間不准他駕駛，案件押後至5月27日審訊。<br />\n<br />\n控方透露將傳<span class=\"red\">召隧道公司經理作證人</span>，以及閉路電視和車輛拍攝的片段。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指，郭與另一司機互不相識，無組織犯案。羅官即時截停並質疑<span class=\"red\">被告響應網上呼籲，不能稱作無組織。</span>"},{"pid":"2a3c3799ffd9f8a9d25719462bc379c75d142338","tid":2447694,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:14:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210315/HUNVJPVO3RFDLIXND2LKPBS4LQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210315%2FHUNVJPVO3RFDLIXND2LKPBS4LQ%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDg1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=070422e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210315%2FHUNVJPVO3RFDLIXND2LKPBS4LQ%2F&h=95e4d30d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210315/HUNVJPVO3RFDLIXND2LKPBS4LQ/</a>"},{"pid":"279c94705bb40497353f291df1a112bc01c2305f","tid":2447694,"uid":77196,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:15:55.000Z","msg":"幾時屯公炒車都告呢條罪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4b7aa05dc0fd5c972f55dbededd20488d58c34","tid":2447694,"uid":230530,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"紅隧有邊日唔慢駛？支持三萬即刻落隧道拉人"},{"pid":"edfbb1f4696c39ada1bdeb05aa1639b5a6c630e3","tid":2447694,"ui